title: Can't see my own club?
body:
Hello, i just came back from a longer break and noticed, the club i created has disappeared for me and i cant see it anywhere, even though my friends still can, and also see my as the owner.

club name: Witchcraft
club tag:  (no tag since it's only 4 people) 

Can anyone help me please?

replies.body: Booped!  You should be able to see it after a re-log!
